OL,3,CThe Border Union Show returns with
OL,4,Cthousands expected to visit
OL,6,FThe Border Union Show has returned to
OL,7,FSpringwood Park on Friday 24 and
OL,8,FSaturday 25 July, with an expected
OL,9,F12,000 visitors.
OL,11,FThe Scottish Borders agricultural
OL,12,Fevent offers a showcase of rural life,
OL,13,Ffeaturing over 500 open competitions
OL,14,Ffor horses, livestock, and industrial
OL,15,Farts.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
