OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1784897315
OL,3,CThe Border Union Show returns with
OL,4,Cthousands expected to visit
OL,6,FVisitors will be able to browse more
OL,7,Fthan 200 trade stands - offering
OL,8,Feverything from state-of-the-art
OL,9,Ftractors to local produce - while
OL,10,Fenjoying live cookery demonstrations
OL,11,Fand family entertainment.
OL,13,FAt the heart of this year's show is a
OL,14,Fstrong political and economic focus.
OL,15,FFirst Minister John Swinney is set to
OL,16,Fvisit the newly established Farming
OL,17,FHub, to engage directly with local
OL,18,Ffarmers regarding the Scottish
OL,19,FGovernment's forthcoming Rural Renewal
OL,20,FBill.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
