OL,3,CThe Border Union Show returns with
OL,4,Cthousands expected to visit
OL,6,FFuture-proofing the industry is a
OL,7,Fcentral theme for this year's event.
OL,9,F"The Border Union Show is much more
OL,10,Fthan an agricultural show - it's a
OL,11,Fcelebration of our rural communities,
OL,12,Fthe people who produce our food and
OL,13,Fthe businesses that support them,"
OL,14,Fsaid Society Secretary Jacq Neill, who
OL,15,Fis leading the show's new education
OL,16,Fevent.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
