OL,3,CThe Border Union Show returns with
OL,4,Cthousands expected to visit
OL,6,F"Alongside our traditional
OL,7,Fcompetitions, we're particularly
OL,8,Fexcited to introduce our new hubs,
OL,9,Fhelping visitors discover the many
OL,10,Fopportunities within the rural sector
OL,11,Fwhile learning more about modern
OL,12,Ffarming."
